msgctxt "sn48.54:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 48 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 48 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.54:0.2"
msgid "6. Sūkarakhatavagga "
msgstr "6. The Boar’s Cave "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn48.54:0.3"
msgid "54. Padasutta "
msgstr "54. Footprints "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.231, sc1
#. VAR: jaṅgalānaṃ → jaṅgamānaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "sn48.54:1.1"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, yāni kānici jaṅgalānaṃ pāṇānaṃ padajātāni sabbāni tāni hatthipade samodhānaṃ gacchanti, hatthipadaṃ tesaṃ aggamakkhāyati, yadidaṃ—mahantattena; "
msgstr "“The footprints of all creatures that walk can fit inside an elephant’s footprint, so an elephant’s footprint is said to be the biggest of them all. "

msgctxt "sn48.54:1.2"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave, yāni kānici padāni bodhāya saṃvattanti, paññindriyaṃ padaṃ tesaṃ aggamakkhāyati, yadidaṃ—bodhāya. "
msgstr "In the same way, the faculty of wisdom is said to be the best of the steps that lead to awakening in terms of becoming awakened. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.54:1.3"
msgid "Katamāni ca, bhikkhave, padāni bodhāya saṃvattanti? "
msgstr "And what are the steps that lead to awakening? "

msgctxt "sn48.54:1.4"
msgid "Saddhindriyaṃ, bhikkhave, padaṃ, taṃ bodhāya saṃvattati; "
msgstr "The faculties of faith, "

msgctxt "sn48.54:1.5"
msgid "vīriyindriyaṃ padaṃ, taṃ bodhāya saṃvattati; "
msgstr "energy, "

msgctxt "sn48.54:1.6"
msgid "satindriyaṃ padaṃ, taṃ bodhāya saṃvattati; "
msgstr "mindfulness, "

msgctxt "sn48.54:1.7"
msgid "samādhindriyaṃ padaṃ, taṃ bodhāya saṃvattati; "
msgstr "immersion, "

msgctxt "sn48.54:1.8"
msgid "paññindriyaṃ padaṃ, taṃ bodhāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "and wisdom are steps that lead to awakening, in that they lead to becoming awakened. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.54:1.9"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, yāni kānici jaṅgalānaṃ pāṇānaṃ padajātāni sabbāni tāni hatthipade samodhānaṃ gacchanti, hatthipadaṃ tesaṃ aggamakkhāyati, yadidaṃ—mahantattena; "
msgstr "The footprints of all creatures that walk can fit inside an elephant’s footprint, so an elephant’s footprint is said to be the biggest of them all. "

msgctxt "sn48.54:1.10"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave, yāni kānici padāni bodhāya saṃvattanti, paññindriyaṃ padaṃ tesaṃ aggamakkhāyati, yadidaṃ—bodhāyā”ti. "
msgstr "In the same way, the faculty of wisdom is said to be the best of the steps that lead to awakening in terms of becoming awakened.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn48.54:1.11"
msgid "Catutthaṃ. "
msgstr ""

